♪The title
of Empress Dowager brings pity♪

280
00:12:22,912 --> 00:12:25,249
♪Palace farces play daily♪

281
00:12:25,814 --> 00:12:27,970
♪Endless plot twists♪

282
00:12:28,539 --> 00:12:30,878
♪That glimpse of you that day♪

283
00:12:31,072 --> 00:12:33,261
♪Made my heart flutter♪

284
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,592
♪Peach blossoms♪

285
00:12:34,816 --> 00:12:36,064
♪Bloom one by one in my heart♪

286
